<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c2">(البرغ)</span> اللعاب<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c2">(البرغثة)</span><a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>لون بَين الغبرة والسواد ببياض قَلِيل<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span><span class="c2">(البرغوث)</span> ضرب من صغَار الْهَوَام عضوض شَدِيد الوثب <span class="c2">(ج)</span> براغيث<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span><span class="c2">(ابرغش)</span><a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>برِئ من مَرضه وَقَامَ وَمَشى وَيُقَال ابرغش من مَرضه<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c2">(البرغش)</span> البعوض اللساع<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
